{"tid":1630694,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 直升機- 紅勵","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:41:31.000Z","uid":279779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"20776c5b02a1b3244dadb0b772c26a3a6db4c1fb","tid":1630694,"uid":279779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14jqhnq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14jqhnq.jpg&h=6f051045&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92YyrfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92YyrfO.jpg&h=3ede2669&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"824d5cf435762d4765538b91c50683095502b6d5","tid":1630694,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:19:12.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cff68171a7ace2527377aa34737bd942946327ac","tid":1630694,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d5848d9f4e8f145fef6e1f537341fd5ca772d4e0","tid":1630694,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"聽到 好嘈<br />\n到底咩事 <br />\n係咪有人面識別？"},{"pid":"1ed52b87323d62782bedbcfbc46225e65e3631f1","tid":1630694,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【政府製造經濟危機】以最和理非既方式 擊敗港共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630641</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf73c037773d771464b49a15f62115efb4ca147","tid":1630694,"uid":101088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f6bb51584b42f936ddd2d0053ffd3d12cecaa11","tid":1630694,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5848d9f4e8f145fef6e1f537341fd5ca772d4e0","tid":1630694,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"聽到 好嘈<br />\n到底咩事 <br />\n係咪有人面識別？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"人群追蹤<br />\n或者跟緊某D車<br />\n有手足響附近D話要小心"},{"pid":"c04533de6fab0c8e7c9a976a18e9b3e68af633e9","tid":1630694,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"Drone出動未？講咗咁耐"},{"pid":"d4dba7007a502545858fb08eaebcdd68d00f0e93","tid":1630694,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"睇flight radar app搵唔到架飛機，如果飛行服務隊應該都show出黎"},{"pid":"9a1599ebf3a0b99baeab2b1e733f6bfbb6679da7","tid":1630694,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n各位小心啊！ ！"},{"pid":"2ba57f7cfebed51ef068dfb7d4f1a6ac5edca403","tid":1630694,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"佢飛左都有10分鐘以上<br />\n啱啱應該低飛<br />\n嘈到癡線"},{"pid":"22ca9cae217fddaa4760ee5378a15aa56b00f73b","tid":1630694,"uid":149397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:33:04.000Z","msg":"深水埗上空也有，已經超過20分鐘。"},{"pid":"a55bb2e96171f32f5deb17faabfbf33b9dccc19f","tid":1630694,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5848d9f4e8f145fef6e1f537341fd5ca772d4e0","tid":1630694,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"聽到 好嘈<br />\n到底咩事 <br />\n係咪有人面識別？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"[重新推出]三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630313</a>"},{"pid":"8c8ed668f24f273236e39c72223e5a3dfc52c884","tid":1630694,"uid":18425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"彩雲都有"},{"pid":"8a2ecdc3da96655e211874611cf1985df6003904","tid":1630694,"uid":279779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f6bb51584b42f936ddd2d0053ffd3d12cecaa11","tid":1630694,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5848d9f4e8f145fef6e1f537341fd5ca772d4e0","tid":1630694,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"聽到 好嘈<br />\n到底咩事 <br />\n係咪有人面識別？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"人群追蹤<br />\n或者跟緊某D車<br />\n有手足響附近D話要小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"走咗"},{"pid":"6c005423ff9977e4f980b5e1b2c9da9b1e3b6c06","tid":1630694,"uid":27